e Professor an der Columbia University in New York.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aGlass construction. 0aGlass sculpture. 0aLight in architecture. 4aCarpenter, James. 7aARCHITECTURE / Individual Architects & Firms / General.2bisacsh1 aFrampton, Kenneth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchlaich, Jörg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062112908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2006z9783110277128oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2006z978311031897508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET KUNST UND ARCHITEKTUR 2006z9783110318913oZDB-23-DKA0 cprintz978376436249240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783764378660423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783764378660/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-031897-5  E-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2006b2006  a978-3-11-062112-9  DGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_AD  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2006  aZDB-23-DKAb2006  aZDB-23-GAAc2000d2014